    "order": 2,
    "width": "6",
    "height": "5",
    "format": "<div style='font-family:sans-serif'>\n<b>Tabela de Regras (Erro x dErro) - saida &Delta;PWM</b>\n<table style='border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;font-size:12px;text-align:center'>\n<tr style='background:#2E5C8A;color:#fff'><th>e \\ &Delta;e</th><th>NG</th><th>NP</th><th>Z</th><th>PP</th><th>PG</th></tr>\n<tr><td style='background:#2E5C8A;color:#fff'>NG</td><td>-30</td><td>-30</td><td>-30</td><td>-15</td><td>0</td></tr>\n<tr><td style='background:#2E5C8A;color:#fff'>NP</td><td>-30</td><td>-15</td><td>-15</td><td>0</td><td>+15</td></tr>\n<tr><td style='background:#2E5C8A;color:#fff'>Z</td><td>-15</td><td>-15</td><td>0</td><td>+15</td><td>+15</td></tr>\n<tr><td style='background:#2E5C8A;color:#fff'>PP</td><td>-15</td><td>0</td><td>+15</td><td>+15</td><td>+30</td></tr>\n<tr><td style='background:#2E5C8A;color:#fff'>PG</td><td>0</td><td>+15</td><td>+30</td><td>+30</td><td>+30</td></tr>\n</table>\n<div style='font-size:11px;margin-top:4px'>Regra ativa destacada conforme erro atual (ver leitura no painel).</div>\n</div>",
